reviewText: It's cheaper to buy this set than to buy seasons 7 and 8 individually! Product was shrink wrapped when it arrived and brand new! Works great and would definitely buy again.
Great price, smooth transaction, fast shipping and exactly what i ordered.  This was a gift for a family member and I would definitely buy this product or a similar product as a gift again.

This is a must-have for any Friends fan.  These are the actual uncut episodes and there are scenes that were never shown on TV.  What a difference it makes to see what never made it to air.  It clears up why the audience was laughing before the actors said anything when you see that there was a line cut before that.

My only complaint is that the cases are completely different on these two seasons.  I have ordered the first 8 seasons of Friends through Amazon, and I always order 2 seasons at a time.  Sometimes when they arrive the plastic cases are exactly the same.  But at least twice now, they have come in different types of boxes/cases.  So my complete set of the entire Friends series looks really odd. :/  And it's harder to store the larger cardboard "boxed style" sets.  I much prefer the thinner plastic cases  The DVD's have all worked fine,and the price is really good.  Just wish that each season would arrive in the same style and size of case. :/ There was not an option to choose which style I wanted when I ordered them.
Bought this for my wife because she loves Friends and always watches the replay shows. Any Friends will be happy owning the seasons to watch whenever they want.
I loved this show when it was on tv. If I could only watch on show, would would be friends.

I purchased these DVDs to add them to my DVD library, as something that many people could enjoy. So far, the main person enjoying my library is myself, but  that's good too. I do seem to prefer the earlier seasons, but all are good, and the season blooper compilations sometimes surprises as well.

How could anyone NOT love Friends?!?!  I watched this show from day one and still remember every Thursday night watching this on the couch.  It got me through high school (and we all know how much that place sucks), college, break ups, marriage, and everything in between.  No matter what I am doing I always know I can turn on an episode of Friends and everything will be all right in the world.  The last two seasons were not as good as the first 8 but they are still good.  I so hope there is a friends reunion show so we can see what happens to everyone.  This is hands down my absolute favorite show ever made.

I actually ordered all the seasons. One of my favorite purchases and my all-time favorite show! Had no issues with the seller or delivery. Everything came right on time as expected so I was able to binge watch with no interruptions while having to wait for the other orders to come. Definitely worth it and I would purchase again in a heart beat if necessary.
